{"tid":2461672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港先生］梁裕恆出100萬零1蚊再讓單手挑戰鍾培生","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T14:37:50.000Z","uid":391580,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"422127481bb9840fe32fd25d90d22469e81c8d0c","tid":2461672,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"自從鍾培生與林作的拳賽落實於9月18日九龍灣Star Hall舉行、宣布門票索價最貴3萬元之後，網絡就此事的討論聲音不絕，繼日前燃燒到杜汶澤身上引起一輪罵戰之後，曾參選香港先生的Flow Leung（梁裕恆）又加入戰團，向鍾培生下戰書，揚言以100萬零1蚊兼讓單手：「K唔KO到要睇佢敢唔敢打。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdoD1tsRNXo1V4SC8VbpSTrozDYigYg4oFs7ozdcpWDhH?filename=TxTS3cR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxTS3cR.jpg&h=a4e6f500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFlow向來對娛樂圈的大事很感興趣，參與討論密度甚高，而最近Flow就在鍾培生的Facebook Post下留言：「小丑，細路仔打交，單手都KO你。」隨即引起大量網民留言批評，豈料Flow再下一城，揚言出「K唔KO到要睇佢敢唔敢打。100萬零1蚊比（畀）佢，認真」。終於，鍾培生都出手回留言應戰，更連銀行戶口都公開叫Flow入數，並列出比賽細則：「就4月頭，入咗數話我知。」而培生亦有將Flow的留言分享至IG，並寫道：「我不嬲都唔係好覆傻仔，除非有着數。還掂都比（畀）錢搵緊sparring partner，留名等走數」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後Flow亦不甘示弱，在自己Facebook連開兩Post稱想應戰並將讓賽升級：「總之讓你單手單腳 唔帶頭套，打贏我100萬零1蚊，攞去，你輸左1蚊都唔洗攞出嚟。」而Flow又向《香港01》記者透露：「有朋友同我講，已經有人發起一人一蚊打x鍾培生，話已經有十幾萬人。不過我唔贊成咁嘅，呢條友咁黑人憎，我唔想人人發起眾籌從中取利，大家嚟留個言 留$1就夠 錢我一個出就夠。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcr6DWZvHFBj78xFy1U5cpmpUeJtdj1VcdaPq6S7Ww7UY?filename=yxNHFZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxNHFZY.jpg&h=7a189f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNX5ZqQAzKQadGLHZqL1cnoj6Wd7jYLezL6K85y6n5PzE?filename=PzRtByk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzRtByk.jpg&h=276b9efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmStL3PzVJws1dH8yjqNzLe4KJ4KPn3ZkPHiG29spArR5e?filename=wDY0sE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDY0sE1.jpg&h=ee8c56d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVih99tW2nPXYkpeR59MwQS69wcub88Xsj6Cs4Tgm7cN4?filename=nsFiej3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsFiej3.jpg&h=14c05406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmceJr4d2PbtUGytsZSPbPvdPHV5pSmp7QejEdsecB5U5a?filename=9E6huTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9E6huTp.jpg&h=7211063b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWq34STUgs9uSNdhnpCHMoQbJu6vT1n36VBuDzwKD3XqW?filename=QvNXuTr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvNXuTr.jpg&h=3f2fadae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQDqm1RzSQJnLtWLYVHUMH4rvAuBumTYZkY6sazXu28Uo?filename=H3967Fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3967Fa.jpg&h=ef5412dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVHGFrqumcuzZkKXsG6FqxCcPHz6ZrsSD7FZe4EhLRwfs?filename=d45YYMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd45YYMR.jpg&h=f5a92c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0dc9114c543bba5f4b4c9c8142c63d31d1b978b","tid":2461672,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"脫獨工程"},{"pid":"883d6d14053f8e6ce9592212d5672dc25b734970","tid":2461672,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"不如姓鍾嘅對家一齊上吖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQb4tbiz1aA35XjnmixjQXEQn7bgm4VWHdYP8LJMyvveU?filename=2stC8YY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stC8YY.jpg&h=9f623ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e572de60ef00098aa1387a946f7b89382ec76a9f","tid":2461672,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"林作：我要"},{"pid":"668be994a82582fe068ae395414f0ae6004213f0","tid":2461672,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:38